    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1249712217973198848",
    "content": "<div id=\"floorcontent\" class=\"b-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-v-80c9ee8c=\"\">\n<div id=\"article-content\" class=\"editorContent\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" data-v-80c9ee8c=\"\">\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年6月20日- </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2025年6月26日，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\">规则预计于2025年6月27日生效，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">核心调整点：修订&rdquo;变更商品&ldquo;场景定义及违规措施。</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">原规则链接：<a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=923540006109319168&amp;btype=12</a></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">修订部分如下：</span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 8.28%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"8%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.92%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 43.78%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"43%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 100.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 8.28%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 100.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"8%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违规定义</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.92%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 100.0pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">19.10 </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">更换商品：指商家在已有商品（SKU）链接上将原商品更换为另一款商品进行销售的行为，更换后的商品在类目、规格、品牌、颜色、型号、品种等属性上发生了改变。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 43.78%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 100.0pt;\" width=\"43%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">19.10</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">更换商品：指商家在已有商品（SKU）链接上将原商品更换为另一款商品进行销售的行为，更换后的商品在类目、品牌、颜色、型号、品种等属性上发生了改变。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 174.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 8.28%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 174.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"8%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">处理措施</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.92%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 174.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">19.2.10</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">更换商品<br />19.2.10.1违规程度一般：搜索，推荐降权50%<br />19.2.10.2违规程度严重：搜索，推荐降权75%，扣除违约金1000元；<br />19.2.10.3违规程度极其严重：搜索，推荐降权100%；扣除违约金2000元；<br />19.2.10.4除上述处理措施外，如商家多次（两次及以上）或大量在售商品出现以上违规行为，或因上述行为引起重大投诉或舆情的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于限制创建商品、禁止上架待售商品、永久限制通过接口批量操作商品、限制提报营销活动、店铺屏蔽、商品屏蔽、品牌停用、类目停用、店铺清退、冻结保证金、冻结货款、跨类目经营限制等处理措施。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 43.78%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 174.0pt;\" width=\"43%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">19.2.10</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">更换商品<br />19.2.10.1违规程度一般：扣除违约金500元<br />19.2.10.2违规程度严重：扣除违约金2000元，违规商品下架；<br />19.2.10.3违规程度极其严重：扣除违约金5000元，违规商品下架；<br />19.2.10.4除上述处理措施外，如商家多次或大量在售商品出现以上违规行为，或因上述行为引起重大投诉或舆情的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于限制创建商品、禁止上架待售商品、永久限制通过接口批量操作商品、限制提报营销活动、店铺屏蔽、商品屏蔽、品牌停用、类目停用、店铺清退、冻结保证金、冻结货款、跨类目经营限制等处理措施。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
